 "\n(a) The research hypothesis is that a high BMI relates to a high blood \
pressure.\nEstimate the linear model where blood pressure is the outcome and \
BMI is the covariate. Interpret the coefficients.\n(b) Calculate ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["R", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1d499e4a-e914-41eb-9297-bd8b3cf62c62"],
 " to judge the goodness of fit of the model."
}], "Subsubsection",
